# APIStreamPulse - API Health & Latency Monitor

APIStreamPulse monitors API endpoints continuously and highlights downtime, surges, and performance degradation.

## Features
- Continuous endpoint tracking  
- Burst + timeout alerting  
- Export to CSV/JSON  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/33_APIStreamPulse.git
cd 33_APIStreamPulse
python monitor.py
